<view class="page">
  <view class="panel">
    <view class="backup-title">本地数据</view>
    <view class="backup-count">{{count}}</view>
    <view class="muted">所有记录只保存在当前微信本地缓存。换手机前请先导出 JSON 文件。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="exportData">导出 JSON</button>
    <button class="secondary-btn section" bindtap="importMerge">导入并合并</button>
    <button class="danger-btn section" bindtap="importReplace">导入并覆盖</button>
  </view>

  <view class="panel section">
    <view class="tips-title">备份说明</view>
    <view class="tip">导出文件可以转发到微信聊天、文件传输助手或网盘。</view>
    <view class="tip">合并导入会按记录 ID 去重，适合多台手机同步。</view>
    <view class="tip">覆盖导入会清空当前本地记录后使用文件内容。</view>
  </view>
</view>
